{"tid":1819174,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港特區護照持有人免簽證前往伊朗","createTime":"2020-01-10T14:35:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T23:20:59.000Z","uid":30788,"like":8,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"2a985c295801638b1e1f0dc9141ce59ef181675a","tid":1819174,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T14:35:16.000Z","msg":"香港特區護照持有人免簽證前往伊朗<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n　　香港特別行政區（香港特區）政府接獲伊朗伊斯蘭共和國政府的正式通知，香港特區護照持有人由即日起可免簽證前往伊朗旅遊，最長可逗留二十一日。<br />\n<br />\n　　入境事務處發言人稱：「伊朗是『一帶一路』沿線國家。在『一帶一路』倡議下，此免簽證安排會為香港遊客帶來更大的便利，並有助加強兩地在旅遊、文化和經濟方面的聯繫。」<br />\n<br />\n　　連同伊朗在內，已有共一百六十六個國家／地區給予香港特區護照持有人免簽證或落地簽證待遇。詳情請瀏覽以下網頁：<a href=\"http://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/service/travel_document/visa_free_access.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fhkt%2Fservice%2Ftravel_document%2Fvisa_free_access.html&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=e7e46735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/service/travel_document/visa_free_access.html</a> 或掃描附件。"},{"pid":"e1138338cdf21a43828fa95144d7cf6e3eeb8141","tid":1819174,"uid":17646,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T14:36:05.000Z","msg":"玩命"},{"pid":"8b5b963f8fbce0a23e7249c50338c2971ac80e1c","tid":1819174,"uid":22974,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T14:37:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dcd5b35c2c6e92bbf03177fdfad8a5e193f614fc","tid":1819174,"uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e1138338cdf21a43828fa95144d7cf6e3eeb8141","tid":1819174,"uid":17646,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T14:36:05.000Z","msg":"玩命"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T14:37:17.000Z","msg":"港共想港人死"},{"pid":"c999bbc95daad67702e247494471ede256fb9cd1","tid":1819174,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcd5b35c2c6e92bbf03177fdfad8a5e193f614fc","tid":1819174,"uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e1138338cdf21a43828fa9